flowchart TD
  A["Sales Rep sends contract (New Client)"] --> B["Client signs (remote or in‑person)"]
  B --> C["System records contract and adds a row to 'ServiceSlips' (Status: Pending Slip)"]
  C --> D["Dispatcher (Staff Approver) reviews Google Sheet, sets Status: Ready for Service Slip, initiates slip"]
  D --> E["DocuSign Step 1 – Staff Approver: verify details and enter RouteNum and Seq; approve/sign"]
  E --> F["DocuSign Step 2 – SS Delivery Team: delivers container, enters Container ID and Delivery Notes; sign"]
  F --> G["DocuSign Step 3 – DispatchCC: receives a copy (CC)"]
  G --> H["DocuSign Step 4 – BillingApproval: review/acknowledge (Needs to Sign)"]
  H --> I["System: saves slip PDF to S3, moves row to 'Completed', sends SNS summary to billing@southernsanitation.com"]
  I --> J["Welcome Email sent to client (Portal links, FAQs, Contact)"]

